43  // UNITS IN INPUT FILES
44  // ... Always use atomic units
45  // ... ... Positions in a0 (bohr)
46  // ... ... Multipole moment of rank k in e(a0)**k
47  // ... ... Dipole polarizability in A³ (Angstrom cubed)
48 
49  // UNITS USED INTERNALLY
50  // ... Use nm instead of a0 and A
51  // ... ... Positions in nm
52  // ... ... Multipole moment of rank k in e(nm)**k
53  // ... ... Dipole polarizability in nm³
54 
55  // CONVERSION FACTORS
56  // ... Electric field (N/C) = Electric field (int)
57  // * 1/4PiEps0(SI) * e * 1e+18
58  // ... Energy (eV) = Energy (int) * 1/4PiEps0(SI) * e * 1e+09
59  //
60  // ... Potential (V) = Potential(int) * 1/4PiEps0(SI) * e * 1e+0.9

305  inline double pTU22c_1x() { return R4 * 0.5 * sqrt(3) * (plambda7*5*(rax*rax-ray*ray)*rbx + plambda5*(2*rax*cxx - 2*ray*cyx)); }
306  inline double pTU22c_1y() { return R4 * 0.5 * sqrt(3) * (plambda7*5*(rax*rax-ray*ray)*rby + plambda5*(2*rax*cxy - 2*ray*cyy)); }
307  inline double pTU22c_1z() { return R4 * 0.5 * sqrt(3) * (plambda7*5*(rax*rax-ray*ray)*rbz + plambda5*(2*rax*cxz - 2*ray*cyz)); }
308  inline double pTU22s_1x() { return R4 * sqrt(3) * (plambda7*5*rax*ray*rbx + plambda5*(rax*cyx + ray*cxx) ); }
309  inline double pTU22s_1y() { return R4 * sqrt(3) * (plambda7*5*rax*ray*rby + plambda5*(rax*cyy + ray*cxy) ); }
310  inline double pTU22s_1z() { return R4 * sqrt(3) * (plambda7*5*rax*ray*rbz + plambda5*(rax*cyz + ray*cxz) ); }
311 
312  inline double pTU1x_20() { return R4 * 0.5 * (plambda7*15*rbz*rbz*rax + plambda5*(6*rbz*cxz - 3*rax)); }
313  inline double pTU1y_20() { return R4 * 0.5 * (plambda7*15*rbz*rbz*ray + plambda5*(6*rbz*cyz - 3*ray)); }
314  inline double pTU1z_20() { return R4 * 0.5 * (plambda7*15*rbz*rbz*raz + plambda5*(6*rbz*czz - 3*raz)); }
315  inline double pTU1x_21c() { return R4 * sqrt(3) * (plambda5*(rbx*cxz + cxx*rbz) + plambda7*5*rbx*rbz*rax); }
316  inline double pTU1y_21c() { return R4 * sqrt(3) * (plambda5*(rbx*cyz + cyx*rbz) + plambda7*5*rbx*rbz*ray); }
317  inline double pTU1z_21c() { return R4 * sqrt(3) * (plambda5*(rbx*czz + czx*rbz) + plambda7*5*rbx*rbz*raz); }
318  inline double pTU1x_21s() { return R4 * sqrt(3) * (plambda5*(rby*cxz + cxy*rbz) + plambda7*5*rby*rbz*rax); }
319  inline double pTU1y_21s() { return R4 * sqrt(3) * (plambda5*(rby*cyz + cyy*rbz) + plambda7*5*rby*rbz*ray); }
320  inline double pTU1z_21s() { return R4 * sqrt(3) * (plambda5*(rby*czz + czy*rbz) + plambda7*5*rby*rbz*raz); }
321  inline double pTU1x_22c() { return R4 * 0.5 * sqrt(3) * (plambda7*5*(rbx*rbx-rby*rby)*rax + plambda5*(2*rbx*cxx - 2*rby*cxy)); }
322  inline double pTU1y_22c() { return R4 * 0.5 * sqrt(3) * (plambda7*5*(rbx*rbx-rby*rby)*ray + plambda5*(2*rbx*cyx - 2*rby*cyy)); }
323  inline double pTU1z_22c() { return R4 * 0.5 * sqrt(3) * (plambda7*5*(rbx*rbx-rby*rby)*raz + plambda5*(2*rbx*czx - 2*rby*czy)); }
324  inline double pTU1x_22s() { return R4 * sqrt(3) * (plambda7*5*rbx*rby*rax + plambda5*(rbx*cxy + rby*cxx) ); }
325  inline double pTU1y_22s() { return R4 * sqrt(3) * (plambda7*5*rbx*rby*ray + plambda5*(rbx*cyy + rby*cyx) ); }
326  inline double pTU1z_22s() { return R4 * sqrt(3) * (plambda7*5*rbx*rby*raz + plambda5*(rbx*czy + rby*czx) ); }
327 
328  inline double T20_20() { return R5 * 0.75 * (35*raz*raz*rbz*rbz - 5*raz*raz - 5*rbz*rbz + 20*raz*rbz*czz + 2*czz*czz + 1); }
329  inline double T20_21c() { return R5 * 0.5 * sqrt(3) * (35*raz*raz*rbx*rbz - 5*rbx*rbz + 10*raz*rbx*czz + 10*raz*rbz*czx + 2*czx*czz); }
330  inline double T20_21s() { return R5 * 0.5 * sqrt(3) * (35*raz*raz*rby*rbz - 5*rby*rbz + 10*raz*rby*czz + 10*raz*rbz*czy + 2*czy*czz); }
331  inline double T20_22c() { return R5 * 0.25 * sqrt(3) * (35*raz*raz*rbx*rbx - 35*raz*raz*rby*rby - 5*rbx*rbx + 5*rby*rby + 20*raz*rbx*czx - 20*raz*rby*czy + 2*czx*czx - 2*czy*czy); }
332  inline double T20_22s() { return R5 * 0.5 * sqrt(3) * (35*raz*raz*rbx*rby - 5*rbx*rby + 10*raz*rbx*czy + 10*raz*rby*czx + 2*czx*czy); }
333  inline double T21c_21c() { return R5 * (35*rax*raz*rbx*rbz + 5*rax*rbx*czz + 5*rax*rbz*czx + 5*raz*rbx*cxz + 5*raz*rbz*cxx + cxx*czz + cxz*czx); }
334  inline double T21c_21s() { return R5 * (35*rax*raz*rby*rbz + 5*rax*rby*czz + 5*rax*rbz*czy + 5*raz*rby*cxz + 5*raz*rbz*cxy + cxy*czz + cxz*czy); }
335  inline double T21c_22c() { return R5 * 0.5 * (35*rax*raz*rbx*rbx - 35*rax*raz*rby*rby + 10*rax*rbx*czx - 10*rax*rby*czy + 10*raz*rbx*cxx - 10*raz*rby*cxy + 2*cxx*czx - 2*cxy*czy); }
336  inline double T21c_22s() { return R5 * (35*rax*raz*rbx*rby + 5*rax*rbx*czy + 5*rax*rby*czx + 5*raz*rbx*cxy + 5*raz*rby*cxx + cxx*czy + cxy*czx); }
337  inline double T21s_21s() { return R5 * (35*ray*raz*rby*rbz + 5*ray*rby*czz + 5*ray*rbz*czy + 5*raz*rby*cyz + 5*raz*rbz*cyy + cyy*czz + cyz*czy); }
338  inline double T21s_22c() { return R5 * 0.5 * (35*ray*raz*rbx*rbx - 35*ray*raz*rby*rby + 10*ray*rbx*czx - 10*ray*rby*czy + 10*raz*rbx*cyx - 10*raz*rby*cyy + 2*cyx*czx - 2*cyy*czy); }
339  inline double T21s_22s() { return R5 * (35*ray*raz*rbx*rby + 5*ray*rbx*czy + 5*ray*rby*czx + 5*raz*rbx*cyy + 5*raz*rby*cyx + cyx*czy + cyy*czx); }
340  inline double T22c_22c() { return R5 * 0.25 * (35*rax*rax*rbx*rbx - 35*rax*rax*rby*rby - 35*ray*ray*rbx*rbx + 35*ray*ray*rby*rby + 20*rax*rbx*cxx - 20*rax*rby*cxy - 20*ray*rbx*cyx + 20*ray*rby*cyy + 2*cxx*cxx - 2*cxy*cxy - 2*cyx*cyx + 2*cyy*cyy); }
341  inline double T22c_22s() { return R5 * 0.5 * (35*rax*rax*rbx*rby - 35*ray*ray*rbx*rby + 10*rax*rbx*cxy + 10*rax*rby*cxx - 10*ray*rbx*cyy - 10*ray*rby*cyx + 2*cxx*cxy - 2*cyx*cyy); }
342  inline double T22s_22s() { return R5 * (35*rax*ray*rbx*rby + 5*rax*rbx*cyy + 5*rax*rby*cyx + 5*ray*rbx*cxy + 5*ray*rby*cxx + cxx*cyy + cxy*cyx); }
343 
344  inline double T21c_20() { return R5 * 0.5 * sqrt(3) * (35*rbz*rbz*rax*raz - 5*rax*raz + 10*rbz*rax*czz + 10*rbz*raz*cxz + 2*cxz*czz); }
345  inline double T21s_20() { return R5 * 0.5 * sqrt(3) * (35*rbz*rbz*ray*raz - 5*ray*raz + 10*rbz*ray*czz + 10*rbz*raz*cyz + 2*cyz*czz); }
346  inline double T22c_20() { return R5 * 0.25 * sqrt(3) * (35*rbz*rbz*rax*rax - 35*rbz*rbz*ray*ray - 5*rax*rax + 5*ray*ray + 20*rbz*rax*cxz - 20*rbz*ray*cyz + 2*cxz*cxz - 2*cyz*cyz); }
347  inline double T22s_20() { return R5 * 0.5 * sqrt(3) * (35*rbz*rbz*rax*ray - 5*rax*ray + 10*rbz*rax*cyz + 10*rbz*ray*cxz + 2*cxz*cyz); }
348  inline double T21s_21c() { return R5 * (35*rbx*rbz*ray*raz + 5*rbx*ray*czz + 5*rbx*raz*cyz + 5*rbz*ray*czx + 5*rbz*raz*cyx + cyx*czz + czx*cyz); }
349  inline double T22c_21c() { return R5 * 0.5 * (35*rbx*rbz*rax*rax - 35*rbx*rbz*ray*ray + 10*rbx*rax*cxz - 10*rbx*ray*cyz + 10*rbz*rax*cxx - 10*rbz*ray*cyx + 2*cxx*cxz - 2*cyx*cyz); }
350  inline double T22s_21c() { return R5 * (35*rbx*rbz*rax*ray + 5*rbx*rax*cyz + 5*rbx*ray*cxz + 5*rbz*rax*cyx + 5*rbz*ray*cxx + cxx*cyz + cyx*cxz); }
351  inline double T22c_21s() { return R5 * 0.5 * (35*rby*rbz*rax*rax - 35*rby*rbz*ray*ray + 10*rby*rax*cxz - 10*rby*ray*cyz + 10*rbz*rax*cxy - 10*rbz*ray*cyy + 2*cxy*cxz - 2*cyy*cyz); }
352  inline double T22s_21s() { return R5 * (35*rby*rbz*rax*ray + 5*rby*rax*cyz + 5*rby*ray*cxz + 5*rbz*rax*cyy + 5*rbz*ray*cxy + cxy*cyz + cyy*cxz); }
353  inline double T22s_22c() { return R5 * 0.5 * (35*rbx*rbx*rax*ray - 35*rby*rby*rax*ray + 10*rbx*rax*cyx + 10*rbx*ray*cxx - 10*rby*rax*cyy - 10*rby*ray*cxy + 2*cxx*cyx - 2*cxy*cyy); }
354 
355 };

365 inline void XInteractor::Potential_At_By(APolarSite &pol1, APolarSite &pol2) {
366  // NOTE Calculates potential at <pol1> due to moments on <pol2>
367  // NOTE Only potentials generated by induced moments on <pol2> are damped.
368  // ATTENTION Call ::BiasIndu before using this method.
369 
370  double phi_p = 0.0;
371  double phi_u = 0.0;
372 
373  phi_p += T00_00() * pol2.Q00;
374 
375  if (pol2._rank > 0) {
376  phi_p += T00_1x() * pol2.Q1x;
377  phi_p += T00_1y() * pol2.Q1y;
378  phi_p += T00_1z() * pol2.Q1z;
379  }
380 
381  if (pol2._rank > 1) {
382  phi_p += T00_20() * pol2.Q20;
383  phi_p += T00_21c() * pol2.Q21c;
384  phi_p += T00_21s() * pol2.Q21s;
385  phi_p += T00_22c() * pol2.Q22c;
386  phi_p += T00_22s() * pol2.Q22s;
387  }
388 
389  if (a*u3 < 40) {
390  phi_u += pTU00_1x() * pol2.U1x;
391  phi_u += pTU00_1y() * pol2.U1y;
392  phi_u += pTU00_1z() * pol2.U1z;
393  }
394  else {
395  phi_u += T00_1x() * pol2.U1x;
396  phi_u += T00_1y() * pol2.U1y;
397  phi_u += T00_1z() * pol2.U1z;
398  }
399 
400  pol1.PhiP += phi_p;
401  pol1.PhiU += phi_u;
402 
403  return;
404 }

463 inline double XInteractor::PotentialPerm(vec r, APolarSite &pol) {
464 
465  assert(false);
466 
467  // NOTE >>> e12 points from polar site 1 to polar site 2 <<< NOTE //
468  e12 = pol.getPos() - r;
469  R = 1/abs(e12);
470  R2 = R*R;
471  R3 = R2*R;
472  R4 = R3*R;
473  R5 = R4*R;
474  e12 *= R;
475 
476 
477 
478 
479  rbx = - e12.getX();
480  rby = - e12.getX();
481  rbz = - e12.getX();
482 
483  double phi00 = 0.0;
484 
485  phi00 += T00_00() * pol.Q00;
486 
487  if (pol._rank > 0) {
488  phi00 += T00_1x() * pol.Q1x;
489  phi00 += T00_1y() * pol.Q1y;
490  phi00 += T00_1z() * pol.Q1z;
491  }
492 
493  if (pol._rank > 1) {
494  phi00 += T00_20() * pol.Q20;
495  phi00 += T00_21c() * pol.Q21c;
496  phi00 += T00_21s() * pol.Q21s;
497  phi00 += T00_22c() * pol.Q22c;
498  phi00 += T00_22s() * pol.Q22s;
499  }
500 
501  return phi00;
502 }

507 inline vec XInteractor::FieldPermESF(vec r, APolarSite &pol) {
508 
509  assert(false);
510 
511  // NOTE >>> e12 points from polar site 1 to polar site 2 <<< NOTE //
512  e12 = pol.getPos() - r;
513  R = 1/abs(e12);
514  R2 = R*R;
515  R3 = R2*R;
516  R4 = R3*R;
517  R5 = R4*R;
518  e12 *= R;
519 
520  rax = e12.getX();
521  ray = e12.getY();
522  raz = e12.getZ();
523  rbx = - rax;
524  rby = - ray;
525  rbz = - raz;
526 
527  cxx = 1;
528  cxy = 0;
529  cxz = 0;
530  cyx = 0;
531  cyy = 1;
532  cyz = 0;
533  czx = 0;
534  czy = 0;
535  czz = 1;
536 
537  double Fx = 0.0;
538  double Fy = 0.0;
539  double Fz = 0.0;
540 
541  // Field generated by rank-0 m'pole
542  Fx += T1x_00() * pol.Q00;
543  Fy += T1y_00() * pol.Q00;
544  Fz += T1z_00() * pol.Q00;
545 
546  // Field generated by rank-1 m'pole
547  if (pol._rank > 0) {
548  Fx += T1x_1x() * pol.Q1x;
549  Fx += T1x_1y() * pol.Q1y;
550  Fx += T1x_1z() * pol.Q1z;
551 
552  Fy += T1y_1x() * pol.Q1x;
553  Fy += T1y_1y() * pol.Q1y;
554  Fy += T1y_1z() * pol.Q1z;
555 
556  Fz += T1z_1x() * pol.Q1x;
557  Fz += T1z_1y() * pol.Q1y;
558  Fz += T1z_1z() * pol.Q1z;
559  }
560 
561  // Field generated by rank-2 m'pole
562  if (pol._rank > 1) {
563  Fx += T1x_20() * pol.Q20;
564  Fx += T1x_21c() * pol.Q21c;
565  Fx += T1x_21s() * pol.Q21s;
566  Fx += T1x_22c() * pol.Q22c;
567  Fx += T1x_22s() * pol.Q22s;
568 
569  Fy += T1y_20() * pol.Q20;
570  Fy += T1y_21c() * pol.Q21c;
571  Fy += T1y_21s() * pol.Q21s;
572  Fy += T1y_22c() * pol.Q22c;
573  Fy += T1y_22s() * pol.Q22s;
574 
575  Fz += T1z_20() * pol.Q20;
576  Fz += T1z_21c() * pol.Q21c;
577  Fz += T1z_21s() * pol.Q21s;
578  Fz += T1z_22c() * pol.Q22c;
579  Fz += T1z_22s() * pol.Q22s;
580  }
581 
582  return vec(Fx, Fy, Fz);
583 }

588 inline void XInteractor::FieldInduAlpha(APolarSite &pol1, APolarSite &pol2) {
589 
590  assert(false);
591 
592  // NOTE >>> e12 points from polar site 1 to polar site 2 <<< NOTE //
593  e12 = pol2.getPos() - pol1.getPos();
594  R = 1/abs(e12);
595  R2 = R*R;
596  R3 = R2*R;
597  R4 = R3*R;
598  R5 = R4*R;
599  e12 *= R;
600 
601  // Thole damping init.
602  u3 = 1 / (R3 * sqrt(pol1.eigendamp * pol2.eigendamp));
603 
604 // rax = pol1._locX * e12;
605 // ray = pol1._locY * e12;
606 // raz = pol1._locZ * e12;
607 // rbx = - pol2._locX * e12;
608 // rby = - pol2._locY * e12;
609 // rbz = - pol2._locZ * e12;
610 
611  rax = e12.getX();
612  ray = e12.getY();
613  raz = e12.getZ();
614  rbx = - rax;
615  rby = - ray;
616  rbz = - raz;
617 
618 // cxx = pol1._locX * pol2._locX;
619 // cxy = pol1._locX * pol2._locY;
620 // cxz = pol1._locX * pol2._locZ;
621 // cyx = pol1._locY * pol2._locX;
622 // cyy = pol1._locY * pol2._locY;
623 // cyz = pol1._locY * pol2._locZ;
624 // czx = pol1._locZ * pol2._locX;
625 // czy = pol1._locZ * pol2._locY;
626 // czz = pol1._locZ * pol2._locZ;
627 
628  cxx = 1;
629  cxy = 0;
630  cxz = 0;
631  cyx = 0;
632  cyy = 1;
633  cyz = 0;
634  czx = 0;
635  czy = 0;
636  czz = 1;
637 
638  // Fields generated by rank-1 induced m'poles
639 
640  if (a*u3 < 40.0) {
641  pol1.FUx += TU1x_1x() * pol2.U1x;
642  pol1.FUx += TU1x_1y() * pol2.U1y;
643  pol1.FUx += TU1x_1z() * pol2.U1z;
644  pol1.FUy += TU1y_1x() * pol2.U1x;
645  pol1.FUy += TU1y_1y() * pol2.U1y;
646  pol1.FUy += TU1y_1z() * pol2.U1z;
647  pol1.FUz += TU1z_1x() * pol2.U1x;
648  pol1.FUz += TU1z_1y() * pol2.U1y;
649  pol1.FUz += TU1z_1z() * pol2.U1z;
650 
651  pol2.FUx += TU1x_1x() * pol1.U1x;
652  pol2.FUx += TU1y_1x() * pol1.U1y;
653  pol2.FUx += TU1z_1x() * pol1.U1z;
654  pol2.FUy += TU1x_1y() * pol1.U1x;
655  pol2.FUy += TU1y_1y() * pol1.U1y;
656  pol2.FUy += TU1z_1y() * pol1.U1z;
657  pol2.FUz += TU1x_1z() * pol1.U1x;
658  pol2.FUz += TU1y_1z() * pol1.U1y;
659  pol2.FUz += TU1z_1z() * pol1.U1z;
660  }
661  else {
662  pol1.FUx += T1x_1x() * pol2.U1x;
663  pol1.FUx += T1x_1y() * pol2.U1y;
664  pol1.FUx += T1x_1z() * pol2.U1z;
665  pol1.FUy += T1y_1x() * pol2.U1x;
666  pol1.FUy += T1y_1y() * pol2.U1y;
667  pol1.FUy += T1y_1z() * pol2.U1z;
668  pol1.FUz += T1z_1x() * pol2.U1x;
669  pol1.FUz += T1z_1y() * pol2.U1y;
670  pol1.FUz += T1z_1z() * pol2.U1z;
671 
672  pol2.FUx += T1x_1x() * pol1.U1x;
673  pol2.FUx += T1y_1x() * pol1.U1y;
674  pol2.FUx += T1z_1x() * pol1.U1z;
675  pol2.FUy += T1x_1y() * pol1.U1x;
676  pol2.FUy += T1y_1y() * pol1.U1y;
677  pol2.FUy += T1z_1y() * pol1.U1z;
678  pol2.FUz += T1x_1z() * pol1.U1x;
679  pol2.FUz += T1y_1z() * pol1.U1y;
680  pol2.FUz += T1z_1z() * pol1.U1z;
681  }
682 }

687 inline void XInteractor::FieldIndu(APolarSite &pol1, APolarSite &pol2) {
688 
689 // // NOTE >>> e12 points from polar site 1 to polar site 2 <<< NOTE //
690 // // This implies that induced = - alpha * field
